blue.lapis.common.command.token

Interface TokenParser<T>


  • public interface TokenParser<T>
    Converts a String parameter, as from a Command, into a game object of type T. Additionally, implementors of this class are able to produce suggestions for completing a partial entry, such as for tab-complete.

      • parse

        @Nonnull
T parse(@Nonnull
                 org.spongepowered.api.util.command.CommandSource source,
                 @Nonnull
                 String token)
        Parse the provided parser and return a typesafe object for it.
        Parameters:
        source - the Player, console, or command block which initiated this object resolution
        token - the token to be resolved into an object of type T
        Returns:
        an object of type T which corresponds to the String entered
        Throws:
        InvalidTokenException - if the String does not appear to match any object

        Get tab-complete suggestions for this parser
        Parameters:
        source - The Player, CommandBlock, etc. responsible for this token
        token - The token to generate tab-complete suggestions for
        Returns:
        a List of possible completions, or an empty List if none are available
